CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 24, 1959, pg. 2 reads: "For 25 Years Service - Atty. Byrd R. Brown, chairman of the Centre Avenue Branch YMCA's board of management, right, presents Branch Executive James M. Burgette, left, a gift from the board of management in recognition o f25 years of service as a secretary of the Young Men's Christian Association. Mr. Burgette has served i n the St. Antoine branch of Detroit, Mich.; Indiana Avenue branch of Toledo, Ohio; Paseo branch of Kansas City, Mo., and the Centre Avenue branch of Pittsburgh. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: James M. Burgette receiving transistor radio from Byrd Brown for 25 years of service to the YMCA, in interior with television
